payload.sql:
SELECT learners.*, achievements_last.created_at AS achievement_date, achievements_last.description AS achievement_description, COUNT(DISTINCT active_trackers.id) AS active_count, COUNT(DISTINCT inactive_trackers.id) AS inactive_count, COUNT(DISTINCT achievements.id) AS achievements_count FROM `learners` LEFT OUTER JOIN trackers AS active_trackers ON active_trackers.learner_id = learners.id 
        AND active_trackers.trashed_at IS NULL LEFT OUTER JOIN trackers AS inactive_trackers ON inactive_trackers.learner_id = learners.id 
        AND inactive_trackers.trashed_at IS NOT NULL LEFT OUTER JOIN achievements ON achievements.learner_id = learners.id LEFT OUTER JOIN 
        ( SELECT a1.*
         FROM achievements AS a1
         LEFT JOIN achievements AS a2 ON a1.learner_id = a2.learner_id 
         AND a1.created_at < a2.created_at
         WHERE a2.learner_id IS NULL ) AS achievements_last ON achievements_last.learner_id = learners.id GROUP BY learners.id
payload.name: Learner Load
